{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-17","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor nosnog konsonanata i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">iang</span> povezuje vokale <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> sa retro-nazalnim konsonantom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ang</span>.</p>\n<p>Počinje sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, gde je jezik podignut i usne su razvlaćene, zatim brzo prelazi u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span> pre nego što završi sa nazalnom zadnjom konsonantom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ng</span>, koja se formira zadnjim delom jezika protiv mekog nepca.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iang</span> je praćeno početnim konsonantima, možete stvoriti slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">jiang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">xiang</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">liang</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">niang</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">iang</span> na ovim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiang</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiāng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">枪</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiáng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">强</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiǎng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">抢</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">qiàng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">呛</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-17"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Li Hong","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_nasal_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":268.72,"finishTimestamp":291.31},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.78,"dialogue":{"text":"iang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":3.58,"finishTime":4.38,"dialogue":{"text":"jiang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.84,"finishTime":6.66,"dialogue":{"text":"qiang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":8.29,"finishTime":9.28,"dialogue":{"text":"xiang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.09,"finishTime":11.87,"dialogue":{"text":"liang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.36,"finishTime":14.22,"dialogue":{"text":"niang","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":15.94,"finishTime":16.9,"dialogue":{"text":"qiāng","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":17.89,"finishTime":18.92,"dialogue":{"text":"qiáng","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":20.11,"finishTime":21.23,"dialogue":{